        "category": "integration_boundary",
        "boundary": "Many presentation‑layer components import SASS files using the deprecated `@import` syntax. Those imports need to be updated to the new `@use`/`@forward` pattern, otherwise the new compiler will throw errors.",
        "severity": "caution",
        "source_facts": [
          "analysis input: Architecture Overview – presentation layer contains 287 components that rely on SASS"
        ]
      },
      {
        "category": "workflow_constraint",
        "boundary": "CI/CD pipelines that cache the Angular build artifacts must be updated to install the new builder package and clear any stale caches that reference the old compiler.",
        "severity": "info",
        "source_facts": [
          "tech_versions.json: Gradle 8.2.1 (used for overall build orchestration)",
          "tech_versions.json: Java 17 (runtime for CI agents)"
        ]
      }
